            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Marcus <lb n="2"/>Sulpicius <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Vepitta</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> mil<surplus>l</surplus>(es) <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIII<supplied reason="lost">I</supplied> <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>artiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>heres <expan><abbr>Marc</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Ulpius <lb n="8"/>Augustin<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="9"/>fa<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>iendum</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes im Giebelfeld Protome, flankiert von Tauben, auf den Giebelschrägen Delfine, über dem Giebel Greif(?). Nach der Wiedergabe im CIL zwischen VEP und ITTA Worttrenner? &amp;apos;Martia victrix&amp;apos; war Beiname der legio XIIII germina.</p>
            </div>
